III COPA BRASIL - 1977 [Brazilian Championship]

First Phase
Top 5 from each group qualified to the winners groups on second phase.  Others disputed the losers groups.

Group A

Participants
Avaí FC (Florianópolis-SC)         Grêmio de Esportes Maringá (PR)
